A

AbstractByteBuffer - Class in uk.co.skyem.projects.Z80emu.util.buffer
Allows you to put in bytes, shorts, ints and longs with different endian modes.
If you are using this with two different threads that set different endian modes, make sure to synchronise the code that sets the endian and accesses the buffer! Use: synchronized (byteBuffer){}
